website_url: https://github.com/epiforecasts/covid-us-deaths
license: mit
team_model_designation: primary

methods: >-
    A deaths forecast using a mean ensemble of three different models: An Rt based forecast, a timeseries forecast using deaths only and a timeseries forecast using deaths and cases. 

institution_affil: London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine
team_funding: Wellcome Trust
repo_url: https://github.com/epiforecasts/covid-us-deaths
data_inputs: JHU CSSE case and death data
citation: https://doi.org/10.12688/wellcomeopenres.16006.1

methods_long: >-
    2020-06-15: A deaths forecast using the renewal equation and time-series forecasts of the time-varying reproduction number; to be updated as an ensemble forecast.
    2020-07-13: The models included are: 1) A deaths forecast using the renewal equation to estimate Rt and project it into the future. For details see github.com/epiforecasts/EpiSoon and github.com/epiforecasts/EpiNow. A timeseries based on the forecastHybrid package and a second timeseries model that also uses cases as a predictor. 
